Class DenseInstance

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.javaml.core.AbstractInstance
      net.sf.javaml.core.DenseInstance
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Double>, java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Double>, Instance
public class DenseInstance
extends AbstractInstance
implements Instance

Implementation of a dense instance. A dense instance is a wrapper around a double array that provides a value for each attribute index.

Version:
0.1.5
Author:
Thomas Abeel (thomas@abeel.be)
